  "plot_summary": "These weren't actually announced in the magazines themselves, but they're worth pointing out:\n\n[HANG0] * Human Torch solo stories begin (with the creators not yet realizing that the <i>Thing</i> would turn out to be the FF's most popular member and <i>not</i> Johnny).\n\n[HANG0] * The reading material was very \"Red\" heavy, with 3 of the 5 stories dealing with Communists in one form or another.",
